，但是听不懂客户需求，驴唇不对马嘴解决不了问题。 低效沟通之后往往还会贴心加上一句，请为我的服务评分。 二是转人工流程复杂，转人工困难重重。 转人工难如西天取经，想要听到客服人员伴着嘈杂背景音亲切的一声您好，还有无数道前置关卡。 经常要反复听到冗长的语音播报，最终才找到人工服务的选项。 将人工智能应用于客户服务业，本该让行业更加高效减少人工客服的压力，如今AI客服却成了众矢之的。久而久之人们对AI客服的不满越来越多。 看到这里，也许有人会问为什么你不能直接找人工？ 另一方面，人工客服的工作时间和上班族天然重叠，工作时间转人工全凭运气，你下班对面客服通常也下班。AI客服崛起后，转人工却越来越难了_腾讯新闻"},"attached_info":"CkEInvG9qcrUsuUJEAMaCTExMTM2MDUxNyC+gui4BjAAOL0BQBNyCjE5MTkyNDI5Nzl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"13 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-51c4d4d04a61a506bbbc03c0d318a060_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"20_1729863206.133956","card_id":"Q_977379628","target":{"id":977379628,"title":"怎么确定对方是可以值得合作的人？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/977379628","type":"question","created":1728998375,"answer_count":37,"follower_count":127,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[307,404,740,1525,115410],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8InvG9qcrUsuUJEAMaCTExMTE3MjE2MiDn17m4BjAAOH9AFHIJOTc3Mzc5NjI4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"12 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-1bdcca02708865b103b4a6748ba0af7d_720w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"21_1729863206.134229","card_id":"Q_663800779","target":{"id":663800779,"title":"马斯克的第三代猛禽发动机真的那么牛吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/663800779","type":"question","created":1723143082,"answer_count":51,"follower_count":142,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[962,7614,70042,153138],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"[图片]"},"attached_info":"CkAInvG9qcrUsuUJEAMaCTEwOTc4ODk1OSCqp9S1BjAAOI4BQBVyCTY2MzgwM